# Trunk workflow (main only)

Verified work belongs on **`main`** and must be **pushed** so CI and Vercel can run.

- Follow **AGENTS.md** and **master-plan-protocol.mdc**: push directly to `main`, do not open PRs for routine work, do not leave finished changes stranded on a branch.
- If you used a local branch for safety, **merge or rebase into `main` and push**; do not treat the branch as the source of truth.

Do **not** use a separate “release branch” model. See also `.cursor/rules/production-parity.mdc` and `.cursor/rules/deploy-verify-before-done.mdc`.
